          class="close">X</span></a>
    </li>
    <li class="checked">
      <a href="undone"> <span class="task-list-item">Buy eggs </span> </a><a
        onclick="return confirm('Are you sure to delete?')" href="delete"><span class="close">X</span></a>
    </li>
